1933;;His Private Secretary;;American;;Phil Whitman;;John Wayne, Evalyn Knapp, Reginald Barlow;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/His_Private_Secretary;;Dick Wallace, portrayed by a 26-year-old John Wayne, has to prove to the Preacher's daughter, his own Dad, his old friends, and himself that he isn't just an irresponsible playboy. Fortunately, his new love, Marion does a good job of convincing them. The question is whether or not it is true.